Simple light and fast SDL viewer.



Just type "lavalamp file"  to open image 

COMPILATION :
---------------

requirements : 
	- libsdl1.2-dev
	- libsdl-image1.2-dev
	- libsdl-gfx-1.2-dev
	- libsdl-ttf2.0-dev
    - libconfig

	Go to lavalamp rep, juste type :
		- $ ./configure
		- $ make


INSTALLATION :
----------------
	
	- $ make install


CONFIGURATION :
------------------

Edit lavalamp.conf in your home directory: 

Fullscreen = [0/1]; (very slow)

Active_Window = [0/1];

